description:
Darkness Radio blasts into a new week of Supernatural News & ParaShare Mass Extinction Event & Dinosaurs on the Moon Edition!

Dave & Tim blush as it appears Jupiter is being naughty, Humans might be moving off planet, Earth is overdue for a Mass Extinction Event, Dinosaurs may be the next discovery on the Moon, plus Psychics, Spirits and Strange Triangles around the world AND your stories of supernatural experiences!

And if that isn't enough...NEW THEATER OF THE MIND!
